  "one_liner": "A rebuilt HOI benchmark — equal instances per class, plus a balanced zero-shot split that re-ranks the field.",
  "tldr": "HICO-DET mixes severe class imbalance with uneven train/test counts, so HOI scores quietly inflate or deflate. B-RIGHT balances every class through automated generation-and-filtering and adds a zero-shot split — re-evaluation cuts variance and shifts rankings."
